  S  O  U  N  D  T  A  P  E

|||||||||||||||||||||||||||||


  Create playlists of your favorite tracks on SoundCloud:

  http://soundtape.herokuapp.com/

  Annotated source:

  http://meleyal.github.com/soundtape/


Requirements
------------

  - <canvas> http://caniuse.com/#feat=canvas
  - localStorage http://caniuse.com/#feat=namevalue-storage


Built with
----------

  - SoundCloud API http://developers.soundcloud.com/
  - Waveform.js http://waveformjs.org/
  - Brunch http://brunch.io/
  - Backbone.js http://backbonejs.org/
  - UI based on http://muxtape.com/


